Your opponent cannot activate cards or effects in response to the activation of "Nekroz" Ritual Spell Cards, also "Nekroz" Ritual Monsters you control cannot be targeted by your opponent's card effects. If this card is Tributed by a card effect: You can target 1 of your banished "Nekroz" monsters, except "Dance Princess of the Nekroz"; add that target to your hand. You can only use this effect of "Dance Princess of the Nekroz" once per turn.
